(301, 'https://sh-cdn.singulart.?signature=2b3e2a6fa44dd33674b381a6a104e25f7326c7a4921b78109b51d12d2ac26006', 'Georgioupolis Hügeln - gross', '50', '68', '水彩', 'Karina Plachetka', '2019', 'green', '82800', 'Georgioupolis 地區被連綿起伏的丘陵所環繞。在前往克里特島和希臘的旅行中觀察到', 'F', ''),
(302, 'https://sh-cdn.singulart.?signature=5b606ac0043a8cb0eeb0be1468291751364c839752b1ddbf52c5e2a5528ff0fa', 'Griechischer Mauer', '80', '100', '油畫', 'Karina Plachetka', '2002', 'white', '211600', '古希臘城牆。在古埃及、美索不達米亞和歐洲就存在繪畫中描繪風景圖案的證據', 'F', ''),
(303, 'https://sh-cdn.singulart.?signature=03830a045fb81a8a41832a6c2b14bc4c08ad0f23dc6b656718ec309778832e8e', 'Gelbe Pflaumen', '26', '35', '油畫', 'Karina Plachetka', '2008', 'black,yellow', '165400', '在一個紙袋的黃色李子。在木板上鋪好的帆布上的油。根據要求，帶有帶黃色條紋的棕色鏡框的交貨見照片。', 'F', ''),
(304, 'https://sh-cdn.singulart.?signature=7736c85d5bb19a89ef0e990dfba57253a5caea4c4370e50cf8e18dbae2f0027c', 'Rote Beeren 1', '70', '50', '水彩', 'Karina Plachetka', '2019', 'green,white', '53000', '採用抽象繪畫技術處理植物，花卉和自然。', 'F', ''),
(305, 'https://sh-cdn.singulart.?signature=971e8e0857070332014150afd1ae56b71e4b3fca5a34b72a719396c10c5c52a3', 'Der Arno Fluss - Florenz', '36', '62', '素描', 'Karina Plachetka', '2010', 'black', '82800', '佛羅倫薩位於流經老城區的阿諾河和從老城區的北向西流入阿諾河的穆尼奧河上。', 'F', ''),
(306, 'https://sh-cdn.singulart.?signature=dc1de18009872655e55811dfbcfa4b5673fa637a5f8012c06f1e33fd15dbb41b', 'Regensburg Skyline_1', '20', '27', '水墨', 'Karina Plachetka', '2003', 'black', '16600', '雷根斯堡天際線的原始車間圖紙。大教堂的兩個尖頂聳立在橋樑和綠地之上。 ', 'F', ''),
